data.description: Great location! Carrara Village in the highly sought after Platina community! All ages! 1st Floor 2 bed/2 bath unit, large & spacious with lots of closet space.  Well maintained, clean unit.  Parking space in front of building.  Community beautifully maintained and has 24-hr guarded entry.  Renovated clubhouse with lots of amenities, includes state-of-the-art gym, a pool room, card rooms, ceramics room w/ kiln, performance center & indoor and outdoor cafe.  Outdoor facilities include 4 heated/cooled swimming pools, 2 BBQs, plus bocce, shuffleboard & tennis/pickle ball courts. Close to shopping, restaurants, beaches, & popular downtown Delray.  I-95 & Turnpike close by.
